E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%94%20is%20not%20clearly%20dividing%20responsibility.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%2C%20our%20biggest%20key%20to%20success%20is%20this%3A%20Agree%20on%20what%20you're%20each%20good%20at%2C%20and%20stick%20to%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20instance%2C%20at%20BNA%2C%20I%20focus%20on%20operations%2C%20client%20strategy%2C%20and%20growing%20the%20tax%20side%20of%20the%20business.%20Adam%20leads%20the%20wealth%20management%20arm%2C%20where%20his%20background%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-retired-to-colombia-got-sick-move-back-us-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epersonal%20finance%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20investment%20strategy%20shines.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20WealthRabbit%2C%20I%20lead%20partnerships%20and%20position%20the%20product%20for%20other%20CPAs%2C%20while%20Adam%20oversees%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-build-million-dollar-investment-portfolio-during-tough-economy-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Einvestment%20portfolio%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20selections%20and%20advisor%20education.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20isn't%20about%20avoiding%20overlap%2C%20it's%20about%20playing%20to%20each%20other's%20strengths.%20When%20you%20each%20know%20your%20lane%20and%20expertise%2C%20you%20waste%20less%20time%20double-checking%20decisions%20or%20stepping%20on%20each%20other's%20toes.%20If%20something%20ever%20does%20feel%20off%2C%20we%20address%20it%20directly%20%E2%80%94%20which%20brings%20me%20to%20our%20next%20principle.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223d63a2bd-9511-4c87-91e4-c00d879f926b%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ECommunication%20isn't%20optional%3B%20it's%20our%20operating%20system%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe've%20learned%20the%20hard%20way%20that%20even%20the%20closest%20brothers%20can't%20read%20each%20other's%20minds.%20That's%20why%20we%20talk.%20A%20lot.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20have%20daily%20check-ins%20for%20each%20business.%20We%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinancial-transparency-parents-talk-money-with-kids-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eshare%20financials%20transparently%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20leverage%20technology%2C%20and%20share%20information%20or%20ideas%20religiously.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20one%20of%20us%20is%20frustrated%20or%20confused%2C%20we%20say%20so%20early%2C%20before%20it%20becomes%20a%20bigger%20problem.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20level%20of%20candor%20has%20kept%20our%20relationships%20strong%20even%20through%20high-stress%20moments%2C%20like%20launching%20WealthRabbit%20the%20same%20week%20one%20of%20our%20co-founders%20suddenly%20died.%20We%20didn't%20have%20the%20luxury%20of%20falling%20apart.%20We%20had%20to%20keep%20the%20business%20moving%2C%20support%20our%20team%2C%20and%20honor%20his%20legacy%20by%20executing%20the%20vision.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20those%20moments%2C%20communication%20isn't%20just%20about%20keeping%20the%20business%20on%20track%3B%20it's%20about%20preserving%20the%20relationship.%20We're%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-flags-bad-business-partner-co-founder-startup-relationship-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebusiness%20partners%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20yes.%20But%20we're%20also%20brothers%2C%20and%20when%20things%20get%20hard%20(and%20they%20do)%2C%20that%20bond%20is%20what%20gets%20us%20through.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cdeaf5d8-be04-4e83-83e6-b82136e10b3d%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon't%20scale%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20it%3B%20build%20with%20purpose%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere's%20a%20myth%20in%20entrepreneurship%20that%20bigger%20is%20always%20better.%20That%20if%20you're%20not%20chasing%20the%20next%20round%2C%20the%20next%20product%20launch%2C%20or%20the%20next%20market%2C%20you're%20falling%20behind.%20That's%20not%20how%20we%20operate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe're%20building%20businesses%20that%20matter%20to%20us%20%E2%80%94%20ones%20that%20support%20our%20families%2C%20serve%20our%20clients%2C%20and%20solve%20real%20problems.%20BNA%20gives%20us%20the%20opportunity%20to%20work%20with%20large%20institutions%2C%20individuals%2C%20and%20business%20owners%20we%20genuinely%20care%20about.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20that%20experience%2C%20WealthRabbit%20was%20born%20out%20of%20a%20pain%20point%20we%20saw%20every%20tax%20season%3A%20small%20business%20owners%20asked%20for%20help%20setting%20up%20retirement%20plans%2C%20and%20we%20did%20all%20the%20legwork%20%E2%80%94%20for%20free%20%E2%80%94%20while%20traditional%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-does-a-financial-advisor-do%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efinancial%20advisors%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20collected%20the%20assets%20and%20the%20fees.%20We%20knew%20there%20had%20to%20be%20a%20better%20way%2C%20so%20we%20built%20one.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEvery%20major%20move%2C%20whether%20it's%20launching%20a%20new%20product%20or%20opening%20a%20new%20office%2C%20gets%20filtered%20through%20that%20lens.%20Do%20we%20both%20believe%20in%20it%3F%20Does%20it%20move%20us%20closer%20to%20our%20vision%3F%20Is%20it%20something%20we'd%20still%20be%20proud%20of%20five%20years%20from%20now%3F%20If%20the%20answer%20isn't%20yes%2C%20we%20don't%20do%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERunning%20a%20business%20with%20your%20sibling%20isn't%20easy%2C%20but%20with%20mutual%20respect%2C%20clear%20roles%2C%20open%20communication%2C%20and%20shared%20value