a%20fictitious%20job%20experience%20on%20their%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20or%20mixed%20up%20their%20responsibilities%20between%20different%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20never%20used%20the%20wording%20ChatGPT%20spit%20out%2C%20but%20I%20definitely%20used%20it%20to%20figure%20out%20where%20I%20was%20lacking%20in%20useful%20information%20and%20where%20I%20had%20too%20much%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sarah%20Oglesby.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENicole%20McCormick%20said%20she%20uses%20AI%20to%20write%20thank-you%20emails%20that%20draw%20on%20the%20company's%20culture%2C%20values%2C%20and%20mission%20statement%20as%20taken%20from%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClare%20Apps%20also%20uses%20AI%20to%20personalize%20follow-up%20messages%20and%20to%20do%20mock%20interviews%20to%20prepare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20AI%20conundrum%20is%20painful%20on%20both%20sides%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BA%20part%20of%20me%20is%20annoyed%20that%20recruiters%20are%20annoyed%20by%20job%20seekers%20using%20AI%20to%20assist%20with%20cover%20letters%2C%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%2C%20and%20profiles.%20It's%20a%20cake-and-eat-it%20scenario.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20everyone%20finds%20it%20useful%20for%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20and%20cover%20letters%2C%20though.%20One%20reader%20said%20she%20only%20asks%20it%20to%20suggest%20possible%20jobs%20she%20should%20apply%20for%20because%20%26quot%3Bit%20hasn't%20been%20very%20useful%20yet%3B%20I%20write%20a%20better%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20and%20cover%20letter%20than%20AI%20does%20at%20this%20point.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20other%20readers%20avoid%20using%20AI%20in%20their%20job%20search.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKelley%20Murray%20has%20heard%20it%20can%20disqualify%20you%20if%20you're%20caught%20having%20used%20AI%20on%20an%20application.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiz%20Stout%20said%20she's%20never%20tried%20it%20before%20but%20that%20a%20coworker%20mentioned%20using%20ChatGPT%20to%20write%20a%20cover%20letter%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bthat%20sounded%20like%20cheating.%26q