ants%20she%20gets%20aren't%20qualified.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20number%20of%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20she%20gets%20highlights%20how%20hard%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquestion-recruiter-starts-job-interview-2025-7%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ejob%20search%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20become%20for%20some.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EVeteran%20recruiter%20Kathy%20Lavinder%20now%20thinks%20twice%20before%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frejected-job-but-got-hired-contacted-hiring-manager-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eposting%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe's%20spent%2025%20years%20finding%20candidates%20for%20a%20narrow%20niche%3A%20corporate%20security%2C%20intelligence%2C%20and%20investigative%20roles%20%E2%80%94%20jobs%20that%20require%20very%20specific%20skills.%20Most%20people%20aren't%20qualified%20to%20do%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20doesn't%20stop%20them%20from%20applying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20Lavinder%20might%20have%20gotten%20a%20couple%20of%20hundred%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20for%20a%20role.%20Now%2C%20almost%20any%20job%20she%20puts%20up%20gets%20more%20than%20that%2C%20and%20sometimes%20more%20than%20500%2C%20she%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20been%20getting%20worse%20every%20single%20time%20I%20post%20something%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20used%20to%20be%20I'd%20get%20a%20robust%20response%2C%20and%20now%20I%20get%20a%20tsunami.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reasons%20aren't%20hard%20to%20spot.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjuly-jobs-report-unemployment-rate-employment-federal-reserve-interest-rates-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejob%20market%20has%20cooled%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20especially%20for%20desk%20jobs%2C%20and%20many%20people's%20searches%20are%20taking%20longer.%20On%20top%20of%20that%2C%20artificial%20intelligence%20tools%20can%20churn%20out%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-job-search-tool-apply-dream-role-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecustom%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20catapult%20them%20to%20employers%20%E2%80%94%20in%20seconds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221baf543d-8ff4-429c-a3b2-2bbaf7bdd47b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20trouble%20with%20'security'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELavinder%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20executive%20director%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsiplacement.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESI%20Placement%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20also%20faces%20a%20challenge%20that's%20specific%20to%20her%20industry%3A%20the%20word%20security%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20recruits%20for%20physical%20security%20roles%20%E2%80%94%20the%20kind%20where%20people%20protect%20corporate%20facilities%2C%20often%20in%20person.%20That's%20distinct%20from%20cybersecurity.%20Yet%20you%20wouldn't%20know%20it%20from%20her%20inbox.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Lavinder%20posts%20a%20job%2C%20she'll%20put%20in%20all%20caps%20that%20it's%20NOT%20a%20cyber%20role.%20Yet%2C%20she%20said%2C%20she%20still%20gets%20flooded%20with%20IT%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20mean%2C%20I'm%20shouting%20at%20them%3A%20'This%20is%20not%20a%20cyber%20role%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20mismatch%20is%20one%20reason%20Lavinder%20estimates%20that%20when%20she%20goes%20public%20with%20a%20job%2C%20about%2080%25%20of%20the%20applicants%20she%20gets%20aren't%20qualified.%20As%20the%20number%20of%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20she%20gets%20has%20shot%20higher%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20she%20said%2C%20the%20effort%20required%20to%20slog%20through%20them%20often%20isn't%20worth%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20really%20don't%20like%20to%20use%20hyperbole%2C%20but%20I%20feel%20like%20I'm%20drowning%20sometimes%20in%20candidates%20that%20really%20aren't%20responsive%20to%20the%20job%20post%2C%26quot%3B%20La