s%20about%20what%20it's%20like%20behind%20the%20scenes%2C%20and%20whether%20the%20infamous%2C%20three-figure%20chicken%20tender%20tower%20is%20as%20good%20as%20finance%20interns%20seem%20to%20think.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2202f67533-aa20-46d1-9ed0-153db4b0110e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20place%20is%20packed%20with%20the%20powerful%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20verified%20all%20of%20the%20staffers'%20employment.%20They%20each%20said%20most%20of%20the%20weekend%20guests%20are%20in%20their%20mid-20s%20or%2030s%2C%20mainly%20from%20the%20corporate%20and%20creative%20worlds.%20Saleh%20said%20he's%20seen%20both%20business%20deals%20and%20marriages%20start%20at%20the%20property%2C%20and%20London%20Liu%2C%20who%20was%20a%20reservationist%20in%202022%20and%202023%2C%20compared%20the%20crowd%20to%20the%20reality%20TV%20show%20%26quot%3BSummerhouse%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20but%20%26quot%3Bon%20steroids.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20emailing%2C%26quot%3B%20Liu%2C%2033%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20about%20her%20time%20as%20a%20reservationist.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20glued%20to%20my%20phone%2024%2F7%2C%20from%20the%20moment%20I%20woke%20up%20to%20the%20second%20I%20went%20to%20bed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20she%20fielded%20all%20of%20the%20restaurant%20reservation%20requests%20for%20parties%20of%20more%20than%2010%20people%2C%20and%20estimated%20she'd%20get%20more%20than%20100%20emails%20each%20weekend%20day.%20Liu%20also%20worked%20as%20a%20part-time%20maitre%20d'%20in%20the%20restaurant%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20people%20just%20start%20piling%20on%2C%20and%20it's%20just%20non-stop%2C%20go%2C%20go%2C%20go%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20All%20of%20the%20employees%20Business%20Insider%20spoke%20to%20said%20that%20the%20environment%20was%20high-pressure%2C%20but%20most%20of%20the%20guests%20were%20generous%20and%20polite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJordan%20Silver%2C%2025%2C%20worked%20as%20a%20busser%20on%20the%20beach%20deck%2C%20which%20is%20an%20even%20bigger%20draw%20than%20the%20restaurant%20for%20the%20weekend%20crowd.%20During%20his%20summers%20there%20in%202022%20and%202023%2C%20he%20said%20he%20was%20usually%20responsible%20for%20seven%20or%20eight%20tables%20each%20night.%20The%20tables%20%26quot%3Bwould%20fill%20up%20immediately%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22895%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Surf%20Lodge%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5755c403910584cc5e8c6e5b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Surf%20Lodge%20is%20a%20hotel%2C%20restaurant%2C%20and%20event%20space%20in%20Montauk.%3Cp%3EFacebook%2FThe%20Surf%20Lodge%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221de3e43d-9cf9-4b8d-847e-e2857b4d5768%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMoney%20is%20everywhere%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it%20can't%20buy%20you%20everything%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20popular%20weekends%20like%20July%204%2C%20Silver%20said%20the%20best%20tables%20in%20front%20of%20the%20stage%20could%20go%20for%20%2420%2C000.%20More%20inexpensive%20ones%20cost%20between%20%243%2C000%20and%20%245%2C000%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20representative%20for%20The%20Surf%20Lodge%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20beach%20tables%20cost%20between%20%24250%20and%20%24750%20per%20person%2C%20and%20that%20tables%20on%20the%20deck%20go%20for%20between%20%24500%20and%20%241%2C000%20per%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cost%20of%20a%20table%20is%20a%20spending%20minimum%20%E2%80%94%20guests%20either%20order%20food%20and%20drinks%20worth%20that%20much%2C%20or%20they're%20charged%20the%20difference.%20Silver%20didn't%20usually%20see%20the%20checks%20because%20he%20wasn't%20a%20server%2C%20but%20said%20tables%20would%20frequently%20go%20over%20their%20minimum.%20He%20wouldn't%20be%20surprised%20if%20some%20tables%20spent%20up%20to%20%2440%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20handful%20of%20high%20rollers%20who%20typically%20end%20up%20buying%20the%20most%20expensive%20tables%20and%20then%20go%20over%20anyway%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20often%20come%20with%20like%2030%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESaleh%2C%20who%20has%20worked%20at%20The%20Surf%20Lodge%20for%20more%20than%20a%20decade%2C%20said%20the%20biggest%20spenders%20come%20on%20Saturday.%20That's%20when%20the%20most%20people%20try%20to%20squeeze%20extra%20guests%20into%20their%20tables%20or%20snag%20a%20VIP%20bracelet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverybody%20wants%20to%20be%20in%20the%20VIP%20area%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20necessarily%20about%20money%2C%20but%20we%20have%20a%20certain%20number%20of%20people%20who%20can%20be%20there%2C%20and%20we're%20just%20going%20to%20stick%20to%20the%20rules.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20long%20waits%2C%20some%20restaurant-goers%20had%20a%20particular%20gripe%20they%20couldn't%20buy%20or%20talk%20their%20way%20out%20of%3A%20no-show%20and%20cancellation%20fees.%20When%20Liu%20worked%20there%2C%20guests%20had%20to%20cancel%20a%20reservation%20within%2048%20hours%20or%20they'd%20get%20charged%2C%20and%20she%20said%20front-of-house%20staff%20often%20managed%20their%20anger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20interactions%20where%20people%20were%20upset%20about%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20understood%20their%20frustration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20money%20flowed%20both%20ways.%20None%20of%20the%20employees%20Business%20Insider%20spoke%20to%20shared%20exactly%20how%20much%20they%20made%2C%20but%20Liu%20said%20she%20was%20happy%20with%20her%20salary%2C%20and%20Silver%20said%20it%20was%20hard%20to%20turn%20down%20the%20prospect%20of%20working%20there%20this%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20same%20way%20people%20spend%2015%20grand%20on%20a%20table%2C%20they%20tip%2020%25%20on%20that%2015%20grand%2C%20probably%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20Silver%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20one%20of%20the%20best%20places%20to%20work%20because%20you%20make%20great%20money%20%E2%80%94%20really%2C%20really%20good%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2283a4dffe-e5f1-4d5b-ad2b-057d8f4f57bf%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELots%20of%20alcohol%20and%20'genius'%20food%20choices%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESaleh%20said%20the%20drinking%20at%20The%20Surf%20Lodge%20and%20other%20places%20he%20works%20has%20slowed%20down%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20and%20data%20show%20young%20people%20are%20generally%20consuming%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-sober-non-alcoholic-economy-restaurants-events-boom-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eless%20booze%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20they%20used%20to.%20Still%2C%20Silver%20said%20he%20saw%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbaby-boomers-alcohol-intake-booze-wine-drinking-gen-z-millennials-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealcohol%20flow%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20place%20where%20a%20lot%20of%20drinking%20is%2C%20so%20obviously%2C%20every%20once%20in%20a%20while%2C%20you're%20going%20to%20get%20some%20difficult%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20those%20instances%20were%20rare.%20%26quot%3BIn%20those%20situations%2C%20security%20is%20typically%20handling%20all%20of%20that%20stuff.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20people%20are%20drinking%2C%20they%20often%20need%20something%20to%20sop%20up%20the%20alcohol.%20For%20many%20at%20The%20Surf%20Lodge%2C%20that%20means%20chicken%20tenders%20%E2%80%94%20sometimes%20an%20entire%20tower%20of%20them.%20The%20Surf%20Lodge%20told%20Business%20Insider%20a%20tower%20costs%20%24145%2C%20and%20Silver%20said%20it's%20%26quot%3Bgenius.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20might%20assume%20that%20guests%20are%20talking%20about%20high-profile%20deals%20or%20the%20people%20moving%20the%20markets%2C%20but%20it%20seems%20like%20the%20tende