g%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EVoigt%20at%20the%20Miss%20All-American%20pageant.%3Cp%3ESage%20Media%20Group%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20week%20in%20Charleston%20was%20healing%20for%20Voigt%20and%20Srivastava.%20They%20took%20part%20in%20a%20mental%20health%20panel%20with%20the%20Miss%20All-American%20contestants%2C%20and%20Srivastava%20shared%20her%20past%20struggles%20with%20suicidal%20ideation%20and%20self-harm%20while%20being%20bullied%20in%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20the%20first%20time%20I%20had%20ever%20shared%20that%20in%20a%20pageant%20space%2C%20and%20it%20was%20so%20well-received%2C%26quot%3B%20Srivastava%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20we%20should%20do%20more%20of%20that.%20Pageant%20girls%20are%20so%20much%20more%20than%20the%20gowns.%20We%20have%20ideas%2C%20and%20hearts%2C%20and%20minds%20%E2%80%94%20everything%20Jo%20March%20said%20in%20'Little%20Women.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20so%20many%20girls%20that%20came%20up%20to%20me%20and%20Uma%20after%20the%20panel%20and%20thanked%20us%20for%20talking%20about%20those%20things%2C%20because%20they%20do%20relate%2C%26quot%3B%20Voigt%20added.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20touting%20women's%20empowerment%2C%20you%20have%20to%20empower%20the%20women%20to%20talk%20about%20these%20hard%20things.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVoigt%20and%20Srivastava%20credit%20pageantry%20for%20giving%20them%20the%20confidence%20to%20speak%20up.%20It's%20why%20they%20still%20believe%20in%20the%20future%20of%20pageants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20makes%20me%20emotional%20to%20remember%20the%20girl%20that%20I%20was%20when%20I%20first%20started%20because%20I%20was%20so%20shy%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Voigt%2C%20who%20began%20competing%20when%20she%20was%2016.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20so%20grateful%20for%20my%20whole%20journey%2C%20and%20that%20we're%20coming%20at%20this%20full-circle%20moment%20and%20getting%20to%20close%20our%20chapters%20with%20grace.%26q