anging%20how%20they%20learn%20by%20connecting%20them%20directly%20to%20the%20soil%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three-year%20curriculum%20is%20designed%20for%20students%20in%20Classes%203%20to%205.%20SowGood%20also%20offers%20hands-on%20workshops%20for%20students%20of%20all%20ages%2C%20ensuring%20every%20child%20gets%20to%20engage%20with%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20is%20already%20visible.%20Lila%2C%20now%20a%20sustainability%20enthusiast%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAt%20first%2C%20I%20thought%20farming%20was%20just%20dirt%20and%20bugs.%20But%20after%20resowing%20seeds%20three%20or%20four%20times%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F471133%2Flow-maintenance-monsoon-plants-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinally%20seeing%20them%20grow%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20felt%20a%20sense%20of%20victory.%20It%20taught%20me%20patience%20and%20to%20never%20give%20up.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20convinced%20my%20family%20to%20stop%20using%20foil%20to%20wrap%20food%20and%20started%20growing%20microgreens%20in%20discarded%20containers.%20SowGood%20made%20me%20realise%20every%20small%20action%20counts.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEducators%20echo%20this%20transformation.%20Indu%20Batra%2C%20Principal%20of%20an%20MCD%20school%20in%20Andrews%20Ganj%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20take%20ownership%20of%20their%20farms.%20Their%20enthusiasm%20spreads%20to%20the%20whole%20school.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeema%20Sharma%2C%20a%20teacher%20at%20an%20MCD%20school%20in%20Sultanpur%2C%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20students%20now%20segregate%20waste%20and%20use%20steel%20lunchboxes%20instead%20of%20plastic.%20These%20are%20lasting%20habits.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebet