%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-9_11zon-1754545373.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22New%20papaya%20variety%20by%20Bengal%20farmer%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-9_11zon-1754545373.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-9_11zon-1754545373-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-9_11zon-1754545373-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-9_11zon-1754545373-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-9_11zon-1754545373-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-482925%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHalder%20nurtures%20each%20plant%20with%20mustard%20flakes%2C%20groundnut%20flakes%2C%20and%20urea.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20credits%20Bidhan%20Chandra%20Krishi%20Viswavidyalaya%20(BCKV)%20for%20helping%20him%20with%20soil%20preparation%2C%20vermicompost%2C%20and%20organic%20fertilisers.%20%E2%80%9CDr%20D.%20K.%20Ghosh%20of%20BCKV%20invited%20me%20to%20their%20sessions.%20I%20learnt%20how%20to%20identify%20and%20treat%20sick%20plants%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20helped%20me%20immensely%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAlmost%20in%20the%20army%2C%20but%20chose%20the%20soil%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201976%2C%20Halder%20was%20selected%20for%20the%20army%20and%20police%20but%20turned%20both%20down.%20%E2%80%9CFarming%20gives%20me%20joy.%20Other%20jobs%20come%20with%20too%20many%20drawbacks%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Halder%2C%20the%20third%20of