r%20size%20leakage%20that%20contaminated%20the%20spawns%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSometimes%2C%20I%20get%20discouraged%20by%20such%20situations%20and%20I%20feel%20like%20quitting.%20But%20then%20I%20look%20back%20at%20my%20journey%20and%20I%20feel%20overwhelmed%20to%20have%20come%20so%20far.%20I%20have%20a%20commerce%20background%20and%20the%20first%20time%20I%20saw%20a%20test%20tube%20was%20during%20my%20training.%20Such%20small%20achievements%20motivate%20me%20to%20strive%20for%20the%20success%20of%20my%20company.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20now%20I%C2%A0do%20not%20keep%20a%20plan%20B%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShanker%20has%20also%20been%20conferred%20with%20Progressive%20%26amp%3B%20Innovative%20Farmer%20awards%20by%20the%20Rajasthan%20government%20in%202019%20and%20Innovative%20Agricultural%20Startup%20by%20the%20Startup%20India%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAll%20images%20courtesy%20Shanker%20Meen%3C%2Fem%3Ea%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1754636423000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjeevan-mushroom-3-1705068511.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D482406%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20MBA%20dropout%20in%20Jaipur%20launched%20Jeevan%20Mushroom%20in%202017%20to%20fill%20a%20gap%20in%20spawn%20availability.%20Today%20he%20runs%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20commercial%20mushroom%20spawn%20lab%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20produces%2080%20tonnes%20per%20month%2C%20supports%20export%20markets%2C%20and%20trains%20aspiring%20growers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F482406%2Fjeevan-mushroom-rajasthan-spawn-lab-startup%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20August%20is%20the%20Best%20Time%20to%20Reset%20Your%20Garden%20and%20How%20to%20Do%20It%20in%205%20Steps%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem