om%20creating%20natural%20fertilisers%20to%20setting%20up%20efficient%20irrigation%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20they%20developed%20value-added%20products%20like%20coconut%20oil%20and%20ghee%2C%20all%20produced%20at%20their%20farm%2C%20Deesan%20Farms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20a%20model%20organic%20farm%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaravanan%E2%80%99s%20family%20owns%2036%20acres%20of%20land%20where%20they%20primarily%20grew%20coconuts.%20Although%20they%20practised%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352674%2Fgrow-bags-growing-vegetables-eyyo-kuriakose-kottayam-kerala-organic-farming-drip-irrigation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorganic%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20input%20costs%20were%20very%20high.%20Upon%20returning%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20the%2039-year-old%20did%20was%20to%20implement%20integrated%20farming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesan-2-1721657645.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Saravanan%20has%20made%20his%20farm%20self-sufficient%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesan-2-1721657645.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesan-2-1721657645-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesan-2-1721657645-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesan-2-1721657645-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesan-2-1721657645-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-357935%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22