ing%20manure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201024px)%20100vw%2C%201024px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesankids-1721657924.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Students%20learning%20farming%20at%20Deesan%20Farms%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesankids-1721657924.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesankids-1721657924-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesankids-1721657924-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesankids-1721657924-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesankids-1721657924-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-357939%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EStudents%20learning%20farming%20at%20Deesan%20Farms%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20farm%2C%20named%20after%20his%20father%2C%20Jagadeeshan%20is%20today%20a%20model%20farm%2C%20visited%20by%20thousands.%20He%20has%20also%20been%20recognised%20by%20the%20Kerala%20Government%20for%20his%20efforts%20in%20organic%20farming.%20He%20has%20been%20awarded%20the%20Kera%20Kesari%20Award%20in%202017%2C%20the%20Yuva%20Kesari%20Award%20in%202019%2C%20and%20the%20Akshayasree%20Award%202022-23%20for%20Best%20Organic%20Farming%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20his%20farm%20was%20set%20up%20and%20started%20running%20smoothly%2C%20he%20was%20filled%20with%20the%20desire%20to%20share%20his%20knowledge%20with%20the%20next%20generation.%20%E2%80%9CMerely%20one%20person%20practising%20a%20sustainable%20model%20of%20farming%20is%20of%20no%20good%20if%20that%20information%20is%20not%20shared.%